(4605, 'Ezapril 10mg 30 tablets', 'ايزابريل 10مجم 30 قرص', '37.5', '54', 'Enalapril', 'Multi-apex', 'Tablet', 'أقراص', 'علاج ارتفاع الدهون الثلاثية بالدم -- علاج ارتفاع الكوليسترول بالدم -- الحفاظ علي صحة القلب', 'Antihypertensive.ace', '10mg', 'Indicated for the management of essential or renovascular hypertension [L6586] as monotherapy or in combination with other antihypertensive agents, such as thiazide diuretics, for an additive effect.[label]
Indicated for the treatment of symptomatic congestive heart failure, usually in combination with diuretics and digitalis.[label]
