(13352, 'Acne free 0.05% cream 30 gm', 'اكني فري 0.05% كريم 30 جرام', '20', '27', 'Tretinoin', 'Amoun', 'Cream', 'كريم', '1- علاج حب الشباب ومنع ظهوره مرة أخرى.', 'Anti-acne', '0.05%', 'Oral tretinoin is indicated for induction of remission in adults and pediatric patients one year of age and older with acute promyelocytic leukemia (APL), characterized by the presence of t(15;17) translocation or presence of PML/RARα gene expression and who are refractory to or who have relapsed from anthracycline chemotherapy or for whom anthracycline-based chemotherapy is contraindicated.[L45349]
Topical tretinoin is also indicated alone [L45389] or in combination with [benzoyl peroxide] [L34869] or [clindamycin] [L45384] for the treatment of acne vulgaris. It is also used in prescription and over-the-counter for treating various skin conditions such as melasma,[L45394] hyperpigmentation,[A257474] and photoaging [A258180] alone or in combination with other drugs.', '6221025002860', '', 5904, '2024-12-12', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
